data.description: Ask about 2.75% VA assumable mortgage! Charming full brick home conveniently located in Meridianville! Large Family Room with trey ceiling, hardwood floors and fireplace. Eat-in Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash and ample cabinet & countertop space. Formal Dining with hardwood floors. Isolated Master Bedroom offers trey ceiling, walk-in closet and Glam Bath with double vanity, separate shower and whirlpool tub. Spacious secondary bedrooms. Large laundry/mudroom offers great flex space. Oversized backyard with patio, privacy fence, above ground swimming pool and firepit. Don't miss all this home has to offer!
